<section class="block-section story">
  <span class="section-tag">Story</span>
  <h2>Why this block matters</h2>
  <p class="sub">Today the AI source gets the same treatment as the human sources — and gets its own Documentation Template.</p>
  <p>You've OPVL'd traditional sources. Today you do the same to an AI tool used on your dossier topic — AND you complete your first <a href="/foundations/ai-documentation-protocol/">AI Documentation Template</a> entry on it. The Documentation Template isn't a separate assignment; it's how you show your AI use honestly — and a complete template protects you.</p>
  <p>The block ends with a cross-source synthesis: where do your sources agree, where do they disagree, and what does the disagreement tell you about the topic? That synthesis is the spine of the Dossier — not a list of three OPVLs — an argument built on them.</p>
</section>

